Mark E
Birmingham, UK95 contributions
Stunning
Jun 2017 ‚Ä¢ Couples
I have done a separate review of Dragon Legend 2 who we did our 2 day one night trip with, which was booked through BestPrice.vn. Ha Long bay is stunning, the reason we booked Dragon Legend 2 is all other boats follow each other on a specied route so you can get 10 or twenty boats in view at any one time. DL2 goes on a completely different route no other boats come this way so you always have peace and tranquility to enjoy the stunning scenery. The DL2 also is only boat (I think) with swimming pool on board. The scenery during the daytime and sunrise and sunset is truly stunning and you get very close to the rock formations. The sea is very calm and is almost like a duck pond. A must see if in Hanoi.
